The paper deals with the optimization and configuration of convolutional neural networks for image classification tasks, which falls under the domains of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Efficient Global Optimization (EGO) algorithm also suggests a focus on optimization and search algorithms, which could fall under the categories of neural networks (cs.NE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
